<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12054c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12054c">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12054c"> 54(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> molten bells</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">A peine ces cloches furent-elles install&eacute;es, qu&apos;un incendie, &laquo;allum&eacute; par une bande de canailles et de fripons de la ville d&apos;Avranches d&eacute;truisit le monast&egrave;re&raquo;. On put, cette fois, pr&eacute;server l&apos;&eacute;glise. Malheureusement, l&apos;incendie de 1300, occasionn&eacute; par le tonnerre, fut d&eacute;sastreux pour l&apos;abbaye: &laquo;La foudre, dit D. Huynes, &eacute;crasa l&apos;&eacute;glise; toutes les cloches furent fondues; les toits du dortoir et des autres logis furent br&ucirc;l&eacute;s et les charbons, tombant sur la ville, ne laiss&egrave;rent aucune maison sur pied. Il semblait qu&apos;on ne devait plus penser &agrave; reb&acirc;tir si magnifiquement ce monast&egrave;re, br&ucirc;l&eacute; d&eacute;j&agrave; cinq fois et que c&apos;&eacute;tait un signe manifeste que Dieu n&apos;aimait pas ces splendides &eacute;difices.&raquo; <br><font color="green">[The bells had only just been installed when a fire &ldquo;set by a crowd of scoundrels and rogues of the city of Avranches destroyed the monastery.&rdquo; This time one could save the church. Unfortunately the fire of 1300, the result of a thunderstorm, destroyed the abbey: &ldquo;Lightning, says D. Huynes, destroyed the church: <mark>all the bells were molten</mark>; the roods of the sleeping quarters and the other dwellings were burned and the coals, which fell on the town, did not leave a single house intact. It seemed impossible to rebuild such a magnificent monastery, burnt five times already, and that it was a clear sign that God did not like such splendid buildings.&rdquo;]</font> <small> &Eacute;tienne Dupont, <a name="SMIN" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#SMIN"><cite title="source">Le Mont Saint-Michel Inconnu</cite></a> (1912) 90</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
